videos.description: Running back Malik Williams sprints for a 46-yard touchdown as the Cardinals waste no time getting on the board.
videos.headline: Louisville scores 36 seconds into game

videos.description: Jaire Alexander intercepts a Zack Mahoney pass, and displays beautiful footwork keeping his feet in bounds.
videos.headline: Louisville defense forces turnover

videos.description: Sean Riley catches a pass from quarterback Zack Mahoney after it is tipped up into the air by a defender.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Riley completes tip drill

videos.description: Louisville's Lamar Jackson takes the keeper, stiff-arming a defender on his way into the end zone.
videos.headline: Jackson keeps it for 43-yard TD run

videos.description: Reggie Bonnafon takes the pitch from Lamar Jackson and goes 33 yards untouched for the score in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Louisville's Bonnafon takes pitch 33 yards for TD

videos.description: Chucky Williams intercepts a bad pass from Zack Mahoney in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Louisville's Williams picks off Mahoney

videos.description: Cardinals QB Lamar Jackson connects with Jaylen Smith for a 72-yard touchdown pass, as Louisville pulls away in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Lamar Jackson hits Smith for 72-yard TD

videos.description: Cardinals QB Lamar Jackson throws a 34-yard strike to Reggie Bonnafon who takes it in for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Lamar Jackson throws second TD pass

videos.description: Trumaine Washington intercepts a Rex Culpepper pass in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Louisville's defense forces third turnover

videos.description: Cardinals QB Lamar Jackson takes the keeper 19 yards for the touchdown, breaking defenders ankle's along the way.
videos.headline: Lamar Jackson makes defenders look silly on TD run

videos.description: Cardinals running back Malik Williams sprints through the Syracuse defense for a 56-yard touchdown in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Williams scores second rushing TD

videos.description: Cardinals QB Jawon Pass throws a perfect pass to Dez Fitzpatrick  for a touchdown in the fourth quarter.
